  "monster": {
    "title": "Zioskis.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Zioskis has an obese light green body with the wings of a moth and the head of a mouse.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 210     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ ++   </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ++.     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: x..      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\n\n\nYou have about 52% to hit with the +9 trident of Certain Death.\nIt has about 28% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage    \nHit     19 (base 29)  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeted by:\n  your spectral shadow demon\n  your spectral Executioner\n  your spectral smoke demon\n  your spectral shadow demon\n  your spectral orange demon\n  your spectral shadow demon\n  your spectral smoke demon\n  your spectral Hell Sentinel\n  your spectral chaos spawn\n  your spectral hellwing\n  your spectral orange demon\n  your spectral orange demon\n  your spectral neqoxec",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Slightly transparent:<lightgrey>\n   This creature is normally invisible, but your magical sight allows you to see\n   it nonetheless. This has no effect on you, though any allies you have may not\n   be able to see it as you can.\n\n<white>Poisoned:<lightgrey>\n   This creature suffers poison damage every turn.\n\n<white>Slow:<lightgrey>\n   This creature moves and acts at 66% of normal speed.\n\n<white>Weak:<lightgrey>\n   This creature's melee attacks deal 33% less damage.\n\n<white>Ally target:<lightgrey>\n   This creature is being targeted by one or more of your allies.\n\n",
